latestIgtvVideos.title: New Zealand Vlog 🇳🇿
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Exactly a year ago, today, we left for the most scenic country I have ever been to - New Zealand and all the while I took clippings for making a #Vlog which I sadly never made. But it was fine in a way, as I could revisit all of it in the past few days that I have been editing. Now that I have finally put it all up, I wish I could include every snippet from the beautiful places we visited and the amazing activities we did there but I am afraid I got to limit it to this (You can always go and check out the ‘NewZealand’ highlight in my profile)

Places that I’ve managed to include in the Vlog(mostly in this sequence): Kaikoura
Heathcote Valley
Castle Hill
Hokitika 
Fox Glacier
Haast
Fiordland
Te Wahipounamu - Milford Sound
Queenstown
Ben Lomond Scenic Reserve
Lake Wanaka
Wanaka
Lindis Pass
Lake Pukaki
Lake Tekapo
Fairlie - Alpaca Farms
Taupo
Hobbiton 
Waitomo Caves

Are you missing travelling this summer too? 🥺
